{"author":"RebarBotNava","data":{"body":"CODE MERGED to main — Gerrit change 434 (both gates +1). Phase-3 consumer-swap infra is now live (flag default OFF, no behavior change). Ticket REMAINS OPEN for the OPERATIONAL tail (a future session with live-run capacity): (1) enable reconciler.baseline_dual_write in prod; (2) accrue >=10 consecutive clean shadow passes — derive the streak via 'gh run list --workflow=reconcile-bridge.yml' + 'gh run view <id> --log | grep baseline_shadow_check' (divergent must be 0; reset on divergent>0/failed/>2x-cadence gap; do NOT overlap an A3 live pass); (3) flip reconciler.baseline_consumer_swap=true + run >=1 clean live pass with it ON; (4) capped live heal with bilateral pre-heal backup + rehearsed restore. Then close (the completion verifier will check the operational ACs)."},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"COMMENT","timestamp":1783589597375545001,"uuid":"d3570d45-7a29-426b-bb03-40004b05bb35"}